Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBPrinters

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBPrinters
public class JDBPrinters extends Object
JDBPrinters class inserts/deletes/updates record from the table SYS_PRINTERS. This table will become more important during later releases of the application.
